The Chairman Senate Committee on the Federal Capital Territory, FCT, Senator Dino Melaye, APC, Kogi West has said that he has not been allowed to see his family, his lawyers. He also said that he has been denied food at the National Hospital in Abuja where the operatives of the Nigeria Police moved him to Wednesday.  The Senator tweeting on his Twitter handle said that he was at the Trauma section of the intensive care unit of the national hospital. 